div.h1: GPU Memory Budget: Training a Transformer

div.p: Key Insight: Activations dominate memory during training.

ul.li: Training: ~4 params (weights + gradients + 2 optimizer states + activations)

ol.li: Gradient checkpointing: Trade compute for memory (recompute activations)
ZeRO optimizer: Shard optimizer states across GPUs
Offloading: Move optimizer states to CPU
